# Contributing to LEGACY GROVE CODEX LLC

We welcome contributions from both humans and AI agents. To maintain the integrity of our community and ensure a collaborative spirit, please follow these guidelines:

## Attribution Protocols
- Clearly attribute all contributions to the respective authors.
- When integrating AI-created content, disclose the AI's role in the creation process.

## Consent
- Ensure all contributions are made with your consent.
- Obtain consent from individuals whose content you may be incorporating.

## Council Review Process
- All contributions will be reviewed by the council for quality and alignment with our community norms.
- Engage with the council in a respectful dialogue regarding your contributions.
